paragraphs.text:
-- Order info 
CREATE TABLE CUS_ORD_PROD AS

SELECT orders.ORDER_ID,
       orders.ORDER_ITEM_ID,
       orders.SELLER_ID,
       orders.PRICE,
       orders.FREIGHT_VALUE,
       products.PRODUCT_ID,
       tr.PRODUCT_CATEGORY_NAME_ENGLISH,
       od.CUSTOMER_ID,
       od.ORDER_STATUS,
       od.ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP,
       od.ORDER_DELIVERED_CUSTOMER_DATE,
       od.ORDER_ESTIMATED_DELIVERY_DATE
FROM OLIST_ORDER_ITEMS_DATASET orders 
        JOIN
     OLIST_PRODUCTS_DATASET products
        ON orders.PRODUCT_ID = products.PRODUCT_ID
        JOIN 
     PRODUCT_CATEGORY_NAME_TRANSLATION tr
        ON tr.PRODUCT_CATEGORY_NAME = products.PRODUCT_CATEGORY_NAME
        JOIN
     OLIST_ORDERS_DATASET od
        ON orders.ORDER_ID = od.ORDER_ID

-- Most bought items across year

SELECT EXTRACT(year FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP) as yr,
       PRODUCT_CATEGORY_NAME_ENGLISH,
       SUM(ORDER_ITEM_ID) as NUM_PURCHASED
FROM CUS_ORD_PROD

-- Average purchasing value per order
SELECT
       ROUND((SUM(ORDER_ITEM_ID * PRICE) / COUNT(ORDER_ID)),3) as PURCHASED_VALUE,
       EXTRACT(month FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP) as MONTH,
       EXTRACT(year FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP) as YEAR
 FROM CUS_ORD_PROD
 GROUP BY EXTRACT(year FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP), EXTRACT(month FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP)
 ORDER BY YEAR DESC

-- Buying frequency overall

SELECT 
       EXTRACT(year FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP) as YEAR,
       EXTRACT(month FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP) as MONTH,
       COUNT(ORDER_ID) as COUNT
FROM CUS_ORD_PROD 
         JOIN 
     OLIST_CUSTOMERS_DATASET ON CUS_ORD_PROD.CUSTOMER_ID = OLIST_CUSTOMERS_DATASET.CUSTOMER_ID
GROUP BY EXTRACT(year FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP),  EXTRACT(month FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP)

SELECT OLIST_CUSTOMERS_DATASET.CUSTOMER_ID,
       EXTRACT(year FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP) as YEAR,
       EXTRACT(month FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP) as MONTH,
       COUNT(ORDER_ID) as COUNT
FROM CUS_ORD_PROD 
         JOIN 
     OLIST_CUSTOMERS_DATASET ON CUS_ORD_PROD.CUSTOMER_ID = OLIST_CUSTOMERS_DATASET.CUSTOMER_ID
GROUP BY OLIST_CUSTOMERS_DATASET.CUSTOMER_ID, EXTRACT(year FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP),  EXTRACT(month FROM ORDER_PURCHASE_TIMESTAMP)
